freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Aggravated maybe but NOT caused by vaccine....chronic issued
Exacerbated of chronic issues not caused, IMO, by vaccine. Just reporting as questions are asked.

I have chronic issues & I think my "normal" symptoms are exacerabated but NOT caused by vaccine. (Had several chronic conditions, some up to 30 years.) Not NEW symptoms, just flaring more than "normal".
Vaccine aggravated but NOT caused by vaccine.
